\begin_layout Abstract
Short user manual of the MatRegister library,
 that aims at performing 2D/3D image registration,
 and registration of geometric data structures.
 The library provides several parametric models of transformation,
 metrics to compare images or point clouds,
 and facilities for optimisation.
 
\end_layout

